    <decisions>
        <name>Check_If_Pre_Surgery_SMS_Sent</name>
        <label>Check If Pre Surgery SMS Sent</label>
        <locationX>0</locationX>
        <locationY>0</locationY>
        <defaultConnector>
            <targetReference>Display</targetReference>
        </defaultConnector>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Not Sent</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Send_SMS</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Appointment.PreSurgery_Survey_SMS_Sent__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>rbSendingChannel</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <elementReference>SMS</elementReference>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Create_SMS</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Send SMS</label>
        </rules>
        <rules>
            <name>Send_Whats_App</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>rbSendingChannel</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <elementReference>WhatsApp</elementReference>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>Get_Appointment.PreSurgery_Survey_SMS_Sent__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <booleanValue>true</booleanValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Outbound_WA_for_Surgery_Flow</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Send Whats App</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>לצורך כפתור ידני על מנת לשלוח SMS עם לינק לשאלון טרום ניתוח (רק במידה ונשלח כבר באופן אוטומטי)
AM: 06012025- User Story 19816- added option to select servay link channel (added whatsapp)
ED: 17.2.25 Monday מטופל קיבל שאלון אחר במקום טרום ניתוח (Add to Get SurveyTaken filter - SurveyCode = PreSurgery)
19.03.2025 Yulia: deleted parameter from Create SMS &apos;ExpectedSendingDateTime__c&apos; for sending immediate
AM: 03052026- 2886891572- add automation name.</description>
